    bf:note [ a bf:Note,
                <http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/mnotetype/relnote> ;
            rdfs:label "This publication originated in <2018> covering California vineyards and wines as an included supplement section of: Slow wine ... : A year in the life of Italy's vineyards and wines. With the 2019 guide of that title, the included supplement section expanded to include California and Oregon vineyards and wines under the title: Slow wine guide 2019 : A year in the life of California's and Oregon's vineyards and wines. The included supplement section continued with the 2020 guide of that title with the title: Slow wine : California and Oregon. Beginning in 2021, it became separately published as an individual publication under the title: Slow wine guide USA." ;
            bflc:marcKey "580    $a This publication originated in <2018> covering California vineyards and wines as an included supplement section of: Slow wine ... : A year in the life of Italy's vineyards and wines. With the 2019 guide of that title, the included supplement section expanded to include California and Oregon vineyards and wines under the title: Slow wine guide 2019 : A year in the life of California's and Oregon's vineyards and wines. The included supplement section continued with the 2020 guide of that title with the title: Slow wine : California and Oregon. Beginning in 2021, it became separately published as an individual publication under the title: Slow wine guide USA." ] ;
